---
import LegalLayout from "@/layouts/LegalLayout.astro";

const locale = "en";
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Data Deletion Request"
  description="How to request deletion of your personal data from Uptake Agency."
  locale={locale}
  canonicalPath="/data-deletion"
>
  <h1>Data Deletion Request</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-500">How to request deletion of your personal data</p>

  <p>At Uptake Agency, we respect your right to control your personal data. You can request deletion of any personal data we hold about you using one of the methods below.</p>

  <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="mt-0">Method 1: Reply STOP via WhatsApp</h3>
    <p>If you are receiving WhatsApp messages from a business using our platform, simply reply <strong>STOP</strong> to any message. This will:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Immediately opt you out of all future WhatsApp communications from that business</li>
      <li>Flag your data for review and deletion</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="mt-0">Method 2: Email Request</h3>
    <p>Send an email to request complete deletion of your data:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Send an email to <a href="mailto:privacy@uptakeagency.com"><strong>privacy@uptakeagency.com</strong></a></li>
      <li>Use the subject line: <strong>"Data Deletion Request"</strong></li>
      <li>Include your phone number and/or the name of the business you interacted with</li>
      <li>We will confirm receipt within 3 business days</li>
      <li>Your data will be deleted within 30 days</li>
      <li>You will receive a confirmation email when deletion is complete</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <h2>What Data Will Be Deleted</h2>
  <p>Upon receiving a valid deletion request, we will delete the following data associated with you:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your contact information (phone number, name)</li>
    <li>Your appointment and service history</li>
    <li>Your product purchase records</li>
    <li>Message delivery logs associated with your phone number</li>
    <li>Any other personally identifiable information linked to your account</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data That May Be Retained</h2>
  <p>In certain cases, we may retain limited data as required by law:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Legal obligations:</strong> Financial records and invoices as required by Turkish commercial law (retained for the legally mandated period)</li>
    <li><strong>Anonymized data:</strong> Aggregated, non-identifiable statistical data that cannot be linked back to you</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-brand-400 bg-brand-50 p-5 my-6">
    <p class="mb-0"><strong>Note:</strong> Data deletion from our systems does not affect data that has been independently stored by Meta/WhatsApp or by the business you interacted with. To request deletion from Meta, visit <a href="https://www.facebook.com/help/contact/784491318687824" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Meta's data deletion page</a>.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Deletion Request Status</h2>
  <p>If you have submitted a deletion request and received a confirmation code, you can check the status of your request by emailing <a href="mailto:privacy@uptakeagency.com">privacy@uptakeagency.com</a> with your confirmation code.</p>

  <h2>Questions?</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about data deletion or your privacy rights, please contact us:</p>
  <p><strong>Uptake Agency</strong><br />
  Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@uptakeagency.com">privacy@uptakeagency.com</a><br />
  Website: <a href="https://uptakeagency.com">https://uptakeagency.com</a></p>
</LegalLayout>
